text: Sunchales Aeroclub Airport is an airport serving the town of Sunchales in the Santa Fe Province of Argentina. The airport is southeast of the town. Runway length includes a displaced threshold on Runway 11. The Ceres VOR-DME (Ident: ERE) is located north-northwest of the airport. ==Airlines and destinations== ==See also== * * *Transport in Argentina *List of airports in Argentina ==References== ==External links== *OpenStreetMap - Sunchales *OurAirports - Sunchales Aeroclub Airport Category:Airports in Argentina
